&gt;&gt;Lusty Town Alpha Version 1 Playable Now!&lt;&lt;

&gt;&gt;Lusty Town&lt;&lt;
<p>Lusty Town is a visual novel where you play as a former introvert trying to regain his social life by rekindling past friendships and making new ones. Now that summer break is over and it's time to go back to school; what awaits you in this seemingly innocent town?</p>

&gt;&gt;Roadmap/Plans&lt;&lt;
<p>I plan on adding more routes/events for currently seen characters and those not yet introduced.</p>

&gt;&gt;Why Pledge?&lt;&lt;
<p>
<strong>Although Lusty Town is a work in progress</strong>, it will always remain<strong> FREE TO PLAY! </strong>That means I rely on the generous support from Patreon donors in order to keep me going! The more support I get from this small project, the bigger the updates will be in the future! If you cannot, or do not wish to pledge, that is not a problem!  I will continue to work on the Lusty Town every single day to make a game that lives up to your lusty expectations! Simply playing Lusty Town is enough support but, you can also do things like spreading the word of this game to others!  I would appreciate it immensely!</p>
